O WHY THIS SCRIPT?
  I really need to quickly restart some applications to make them effective again, such as clash.

O HOW TO USE?
  E.g. python3 resapp.py clash

O SUGGESTION
  You can set it as an alias to quickly call:
    alias resapp="python3 resapp.py"